MAIN_MESSAGE: There is a unplanned power cut in the CW5 and CW7 postcode areas of Nantwich and Winsford, affecting properties in a widespread area. Our engineers are replacing grounded overhead lines close to Cholmondeston Hall and are still working to get your power back on as quickly and as safely as possible by 4 pm. We will update this message if this information changes. We apologise for the inconvenience and thank you for your patience. This message was updated at 1:25 pm on 13th January, 2021.
